nodes.title: Brute Force Made Easy 2021
nodes.excerpt: BFME is IET NITK's Competitive Programming and DSA Workshops, designed to teach DSA concepts and train the participants in view of the upcoming Placements and Internship season.

nodes.title: IET Present Around the Net (PATN)
nodes.excerpt: With the coronavirus shutting us down in our houses, online mode is the only way to go. Hence, we would like to proudly announce an Online University-Level Competition to brush up on your presentation skills.
